entry.title: riconuts/troll-engine
entry.summary:
Engine originally used on the TGT v4 mod.

Friday Night Funkin': Troll Engine

Troll Engine is the fork of Psych Engine that's used on the Tails Gets Trolled mod.

Installation:

You must have Haxe 4.2.5.

open up a Command Prompt/PowerShell or Terminal, type haxelib install hmm

after it finishes, simply type haxelib run hmm install in order to install all the needed libraries

entry.title: FunkinCrew/funkVis
entry.summary:
funkin.vis

funkin.vis is a haxelib for processing audio data into frequency data using FFT's, created for Friday Night Funkin' by The Funkin' Crew Inc.

On web it uses web browsers' AnalyzerNode, and on native it uses a Radix-2 FFT algorithm.

Installation

haxelib git funkin.vis https://github.com/FunkinCrew/funkVis
